reviewText: Go back and relive he show you loved as a kid!!
I absolutely love this show - watched it as a kid - as good or better now.
Fun TV show remember when I was a kid, very creative much better than today's kid shows
Got this from Denver Goodwill. They made good use of their donation. And I got a product with no scratches at a great price. Wish they would do this in Richmond.
Really enjoying this show.  Started with the two movies and then had to start gathering the series.  Amazing what they can do with puppets and the scale of boats, bridges etc.
One of my favorite shows, even though I discovered it very recently, since I'm not relly from the sixties, is very entreteined and I can see the differences with the shows of today. I love it.

I just wanted to say thankyou for having Thunderbirds set 6. It came in great condition and with in a week of me ordering it. Now my Thunderbirds are complete.
Hope to buy more stuff from yous soon. Thanks again and keep up the good job.
from David
